                    <tr>
                        <td class="CONTENTTD" style="font-size: 10px; color: #000000; border: 0px solid;"><a href="http://www.expertretail.com/1/default.asp" style="font-weight: bold;"></a>&nbsp;ERS Australia today announced that is was extending its successful Corporate service to the broader market in Australia. Initially ERS intends to provide local businesses and home owners on the Gold Coast with professional Computer Support service for Macs and Windows PC's and tablets at affordable prices. With many of the Service providers demanding close to $200-00 per hour for similar services, ERS intends to offer the same quality of service at $110-00 per hour, making it far more affordable for our customers. With more and more devices per household and business, we are noticing a growing demand for our Tech's to integrate Mac and PC's on networks. Everyone at ERS are extremely excited at the prospect of launching a new web site to cater for our new customers. Visit <a href="http://www.computer-repairs-hope-island.com/">http://www.computer-repairs-hope-island.com</a>&nbsp;for more information and the service offered.</td>
